    <item>
      <title>决定孟加拉国未来的关键人物</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/the-key-people-who-will-shape-bangladesh-s-future</link>
      <description><![CDATA[孟加拉国经历了一周的动荡之后，临时政府现已成立，开始着手为这个南亚国家带来稳定和秩序的艰巨工作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/the-key-people-who-will-shape-bangladesh-s-future</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 03:55:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯支持取消小费税，采纳特朗普提出的想法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/harris-backs-ending-taxes-on-tips-adopting-idea-trump-floated</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯表示，她将寻求取消服务行业工人的小费收入税——这与她的 2024 年竞争对手共和党人唐纳德·特朗普提出的一项提议相一致，旨在争取年轻人和工薪阶层选民。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/harris-backs-ending-taxes-on-tips-adopting-idea-trump-floated</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 02:50:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>社会党选择冈萨雷斯为厄瓜多尔总统候选人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/socialists-choose-gonzalez-as-ecuador-presidential-candidate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[厄瓜多尔主要社会主义反对党选择社会保守派前议员路易莎·冈萨雷斯作为 2 月 9 日总统选举的候选人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/socialists-choose-gonzalez-as-ecuador-presidential-candidate</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 01:30:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
