    <item>
      <title>联合国大会主席称联合国已准备好调解委内瑞拉问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/general-assembly-president-says-un-ready-to-mediate-in-venezuela</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国大会主席丹尼斯·弗朗西斯周六表示，联合国准备在委内瑞拉进行调解，以缓解上个月有争议的选举造成的紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/general-assembly-president-says-un-ready-to-mediate-in-venezuela</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 00:31:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯表示不会干预美联储 谴责特朗普</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-10/harris-says-she-won-t-interfere-with-fed-in-rebuke-to-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯表示，她将尊重美联储的独立性，寻求与其 2024 年的共和党对手唐纳德·特朗普形成对比，并计划在下周推出其经济议程的部分内容。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-10/harris-says-she-won-t-interfere-with-fed-in-rebuke-to-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 10 Aug 2024 22:49:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗总统佩泽什基安任命道德警察批评者为副总统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-10/iran-s-pezeshkian-names-morality-police-critic-as-vice-president</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗总统马苏德·佩泽什基安任命一位直言不讳的批评该国备受争议的道德警察队伍的人为其副总统之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-10/iran-s-pezeshkian-names-morality-police-critic-as-vice-president</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 10 Aug 2024 21:37:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称微软曾告诉他的竞选团队，伊朗是黑客攻击的幕后黑手</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-10/trump-campaign-says-it-was-hacked-suggests-iran-to-blame</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党候选人唐纳德·特朗普表示，微软公司告知他，他的一个竞选网站遭到伊朗政府的黑客攻击，但他说黑客在此次入侵中只能访问“公开信息”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-10/trump-campaign-says-it-was-hacked-suggests-iran-to-blame</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 10 Aug 2024 19:51:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列称袭击了加沙学校内的哈马斯指挥部</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-10/israel-strike-on-gaza-school-kills-100-palestinians-hamas-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列军方称，以色列对加沙市发动的致命袭击遭到国际社会谴责，袭击目标是设在一所学校和相邻清真寺内的哈马斯“指挥和控制中心”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-10/israel-strike-on-gaza-school-kills-100-palestinians-hamas-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 10 Aug 2024 04:45:16 GMT</pubDate>
